{"tid":1676360,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［太古打手］ 東薈城二期開左啦！","createTime":"2019-10-26T11:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T11:51:09.000Z","uid":89538,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"144e1b7d312518df15f5dff1d5327100b54bcb92","tid":1676360,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:35:40.000Z","msg":"首先太古係香港人既驕傲之一 同埋 咁多示威拒狗於門外唔洗多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n東薈城二期我敢講係比番東涌人一個屬於東涌人既商場！<br />\n<br />\n東薈城一直既問題就係野都無得食 <br />\n全部都係outlet 賣倉底垃圾<br />\n仲要勁多大陸人 <br />\n後期連戲院仲要無埋（呀鼎無撚用dllm）<br />\n本地人根本唔會去<br />\n<br />\n依家二期就完全反轉 好多野食 有番food court 戲院<br />\n多好多新既鋪 唔再係垃圾outlet<br />\n當然都保持一貫太古商場既風格 又大又闊絡 好好行<br />\n<br />\n商場規劃唔係一時三刻就做到<br />\n咁都證明太古唔係因為無左大陸人先咁做 <br />\n而係一早已經有打算做番個平衡本土人利益既商場<br />\n<br />\n請大家多多支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申無收錢既打手"},{"pid":"9666fe568d02f0a1b8161ce7caef765baabf8d35","tid":1676360,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c152cdbbf96d3bd87ab657c8f63caa6ced93e6","tid":1676360,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:51:09.000Z","msg":"仲有免費Wi-Fi 夠快睇到YouTube<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}